    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1022547520">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1022547520" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1022547520" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1022547520">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sodalulu/">Sodalulu</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-03-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">近现代史的部分就熟悉多了，读起来也快些。小岛毅时刻强调着学习历史的重要性，不要走入偏狭的误区，强调透过世界史和东亚史的角度看待日本史，批判性地解读了日本明治以后的发展历程。也讽刺了当代人的粗陋无知。看似语气轻松，实则蛮严肃的，也是忧思颇深啊。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1000427918">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1000427918" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1000427918" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1000427918">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/amyli1989/">AMY园</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">容易被书名误导以为是普及史实的书。其实是略及史实，反驳“司马史观”。太多人受到司马辽太郎小说叙事的影响，将日本近代分为光荣和暴走两阶段来看。要从日俄战争，甚至明治维新那里寻找暴走的源头</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1032567234">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1032567234" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1032567234" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1032567234">有用</a>
