    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7756122/" class="title-link">真话的重量</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7756122"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/RonaldoLuiz/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3839681-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/RonaldoLuiz/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">格瓦拉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-31"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-31 16:55:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7756122_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   一句真话的重量比整个世界还要重。——被称为俄罗斯良心的索尔任尼琴如是说。  《东大爸爸写给我的日本史2》其实就是对索翁这句话的反复诠释。作者小岛毅是东京大学历史系的教授，他希望通过自己的梳理总结，以思想史为载体，尝试去打破传统历史教科书僵化地以政治史为主线，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7756122/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7756122_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7756122_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










